### Setup
- Download (https://www.altera.com/downloads/download-center.html) Quartus standard and unpack.
- Run the installer (.sh). 

### Setting up license

- Add the following line export LM_LICENSE_FILE="link:link" in your profile, the value of this variable can be obtained at https://intelpedia.intel.com/Altera .

### Add Quartus to your PATH

PATH=$PATH:/home/<user>/altera*/version/quartus/bin

### UDev JTAG rules

https://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/Altera_Design_Software

### Build

make

### How to flash

make program

### Usage of logic ports

more aero_fpga.fit.rpt

### How to flash FPGA firmware in Aero using in-system-flasher

Build
Copy aero_fpga.jam to Aero
In Aero "jam -aprogram aero_compute_board_only_fpga.jam"
